{"tid":2217591,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺男人有揸飛機 之類既牌係吸引好多","createTime":"2020-09-25T14:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T16:26:14.000Z","uid":87155,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"31ba9dabb28b5eefc7bc8973b15c07a0fbc435fa","tid":2217591,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:18:43.000Z","msg":"唔係車牌船牌依d垃圾牌 死開一二邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你諗下你條仔係打仗 戰亂果陣 大家都趕去停機坪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個撚個都當個機師神咁拜 又求又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個時候你條仔淡淡定 好似君臨天下咁慢慢上部飛機再開著佢同你講「上黎」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n剩係諗都濕撚哂 究竟有咩牌可以吸引過飛機牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要最緊要有飛機牌既一定90%有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡直完美！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b76c613e87830ce47281c66a2fb95dc60b486ec","tid":2217591,"uid":308450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cc0ea0fcb7335c388091108f7da8e4c85366395","tid":2217591,"uid":297453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:21:42.000Z","msg":"好吸引咩 我日日都揸自己架飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa55671fd8a640d1522ee20dd688099f72e7dba1","tid":2217591,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"4b76c613e87830ce47281c66a2fb95dc60b486ec","tid":2217591,"uid":308450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"